  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Come join us for opportunities to work on exciting and rewarding projects!</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Planning and Design:</p><ul><li>Ability to provide and interpret space planning in accordance to client requirements</li><li>Prepare drawings for proposal, construction and as-built</li><li>Sample board and material schedule preparation</li><li>Documents control</li></ul><p>Management:</p><ul><li>Periodic updates with management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Min Degree in Architectural/Engineering field</li><li>Proficient in BIM Revit & AutoCAD for Engineering & Architecture.</li><li>Knowledgeable in Adobe Photoshop, Sketch Up and Vray.</li><li>Familiar with BCA Building Code</li><li>Ability to work independently in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Effective communication and good interpersonal skills</li><li>Both genders welcome</li></ul><p><strong>Advantages</strong></p><ul><li>Relevant experience with healthcare projects</li><li>Familiar with Structural and M&E drawings</li><li>Good graphic, verbal and written communication skills</li></ul>",
